en_509905_0	A batch of 20 Military officers during a 4-day long workshop underwent training to be potential instructors for drug prevention roles during 9-12 July.
en_509905_1	It was held at the Alcohol Drug Information Centre (ADIC) attended by a lady Officer.
en_509905_2	This workshop was organized by the Army Directorate of Psychological Operations on the instructions of the Commander of the Army.
